src_text: Ditshwetso tse di botlhokwa tsa Kabinete Kabinete e letleletse maano a go tlhoma Khonferense e e Itlhophileng e e ka ga Meepo ya Operation Phakisa, e e tla nopolang setlhopha sa mathata a a popota a a kgoreletsang serodumo sa kgolo le tlhabololo ya lekala len Khonferense e e Itlhophileng e e ka ga Meepo e tla dirisana mmogo mo go tlhagiseng maano a go samagana le dikgwetlho tsen Khonferense e e Itlhophileng e e ka ga Meepo e rulaganyeditswe go tshwarwa dibeke di le nne ka Diphalane 2012.
trg_text: Key Cabinet decisions Cabinet approved the plans to set up the Operation Phakisa Mining Lab, which will identify a set of concrete problems that are limiting the growth and developmental impact of the secto The Mining Lab will also collaboratively develop plans to overcome these challenge A four-week Mining Lab is scheduled for October 2012.

src_text: Kabinete e letleletse go phasaladiwa ga pampiritlhomo ya Togamaano ya Ikonomi ya Tlhago gore set haba se dire ditshwaelo ka ga yon Togamaano eno e akaretsa dingwaga di le 14 mme e tla konosediwa ka ngwaga wa 2030.
trg_text: Cabinet approved the publishing for public comments of the draft Biodiversity Economy Strateg The strategy covers the period of 14 years ending 2030.

src_text: Togamaano eno e senka go oketsa go nneng le seabe ga tlhago mo Seelosotlheng sa Ditlhagisiwa tsa Naga mo Ngwageng (GDP) mme e ntse e tsweletse go somarela thulaganyo ya tlhagMogareng gat se dingwe, e tla tsepamisa mogopolo mo go thuthuseng kgolo mo maphateng ka bobedi e leng la ditshedi tse di tlhaga le la ikonomi ya bojanal Kabinete e letleletse go phasaladiwa ga pampiritlhomo ya letlhomeso le tshamagano ya go tlhama Tseokarolo e e Tobaneng le Maikaelelo a Boset haba a Aforika Borwa gore set haba se dire ditshwaelo ka ga yone le go e buisanela le bannaleseabe pele e ka isiwa kwa Lekgotleng la Matlhomeso a Dinagakopano ka ga Phetogo ya Maemo a loapi (UNFCC).Letlhomeso leno fa go konoseditswe go dira ditshwaelo ka botlalo e tla nna karolo ya ditumelano tsa semolao tse di ka fat lase ga UNFCC, mme e tla tsenngwa tirisong kwa Paris, France ka Sedimonthole 201 MelaotlhomoKabinete e letleletse melaotlhomo e e latelang gore set haba se dire ditshwaelo ka ga yone: Molaotlhomo wa Setheo sa Botsamaisi jwa Melelwane (BMA) wa 2015, o maitlhomo a one e leng go tlhoma BMA e e tla tshegetsang tshireletsego mo go kgabaganyeng melelwane fa go tsewa maeto; o diragatsa ditlhokwa tsa tlhokomelo le tshireletsego ya boset haba, go ya ka maikano a naga ya Aforika Borwa, a Aforika le a bodit habat habBolaodi jono bo le esi jwa go kgobelela go tsenyeng tirisong ga melao ya kwa melelwaneng bo tlhagisa bokgoni jwa ditirelo tse di somarelang ditshenyegelo mmogo le tshireletsego le bolaodi jo bo thathabologetsweng jwa ditikologo tsa melelwan Molaotlhomotlhabololo wa Bafaladi wa 2015, o o senkang go tlhola thulaganyo e e mosola e e dirang sentle tebang le bafaladi ba ba senkang botshabelKabinete gape e letleletse go tlisiwa kwa ga melaotlhomo e e latelang kwa Palamenteng: Pusoselegae: Molaotlhomotlhabololo wa Ditlhopho tsa Mebasepala wa 2015, e leng o o tlhabololang Pusoselegae: Molao wa Ditlhopho wa Ditlhopho tsa Mebasepala wa 2000 (Molao wa bo 27 wa 2000).Ditlhabololo di rarabolola mathata ka maikaelelo a go netefatsa fa go na le dipaakanyo tse di tsamayang sentle le go konosetsa ditlhopho tsa 2016 tsa dipusoselega Molaotlhomotlhabololo wa Letlole la go go Tlhokomela fa o Latlhegetswe ke Tiro ka 2014.
